pullRequest.body:
similar to #19212, but for Quantales, taken from the variable_alias docs.

Zulip: https://leanprover.zulipchat.com/#narrow/channel/287929-mathlib4/topic/why.20.5Bvariable_alias.5D.20attribute.20is.20not.20used.20in.20Mathlib.3F

---

Let's have the discussion about what would be the best way to achieve variable_alias commits in #19212.
I'll try to keep the PR here in line with that one.
Not sure if it is technically correct, but I'll mark this one as depending on #19212 for the purpose of centralizing the discussion.

- [ ] depends on: #19212
